# Title: Prefetch File Deleted
# Author: Cedric MAURUGEON
# Date: 2021-09-29
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the deletion of a prefetch file which may indicate an attempt to destroy forensic evidence
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1070.004
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/file/file_delete/file_delete_win_delete_prefetch.yml

TargetFilename="*:\\Windows\\Prefetch\\*" TargetFilename="*.pf" NOT (Image="*:\\windows\\system32\\svchost.exe" User IN ("*AUTHORI*", "*AUTORI*"))